<span id="freeTextContainer14930830934416100613">Finding Hope in the Darkness of Grief presents Diamante Lavendar’s approach to healing her broken heart because of the death of her children. The poetry and prose gives insight to the depth of grief she suffered, while also showing the steps she took to healing. Her dependent on others allowed her to share her grief when it became too heavy for her to bare it herself. Words of wisdom are woven within her words making this an excellent book to give someone who is grieving as a gift.<br/> <br/>I love that D</span>
  <span id="freeText14930830934416100613" style="display:none">Finding Hope in the Darkness of Grief presents Diamante Lavendar’s approach to healing her broken heart because of the death of her children. The poetry and prose gives insight to the depth of grief she suffered, while also showing the steps she took to healing. Her dependent on others allowed her to share her grief when it became too heavy for her to bare it herself. Words of wisdom are woven within her words making this an excellent book to give someone who is grieving as a gift.<br /> <br />I love that Diamante Lavendar speaks to the soul that is dying inside. She puts into words what only a broken heart can hear, giving it the hope of healing and the ear of someone who understands. Finding Hope in the Darkness of Grief would be useful as words of encouragement and love. The artful work within the pages complements the emotions of this book.  </span>
