    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2454602649" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4301994925626705427">A very quick, but meaningful read. It feels like you are really going into her head and feeling experiencing her thoughts and emotions. I think the message here is finding the bright spots in life after going through dark times. I would definitely recommend.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

