    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2519728007" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2519728007" />
    <a title="Luxurious Literature" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/74338326-luxurious-literature"><img alt="Luxurious Literature" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1532679946p2/74338326.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2519728007?book_show_action=true">Sep 05, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Luxurious Literature" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Luxurious Literature" href="/user/show/74338326-luxurious-literature">Luxurious Literature</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2519728007" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer612877259523051581">‘Finding Hope in the Darkness of Grief’ is an easy to read and gentle spiritual offering from the author. Consisting solely of her art and poetry, which are glimpses into her struggles in life, this book is a haven of tranquil thought, reflection and teaching. <br/><br/>Lavendar has an almost childlike innocence that shines though this book. Her belief that grief can be our teacher and that we can learn important lessons through suffering is proudly displayed throughout. This book is a timely reminder tha</span>
  <span id="freeText612877259523051581" style="display:none">‘Finding Hope in the Darkness of Grief’ is an easy to read and gentle spiritual offering from the author. Consisting solely of her art and poetry, which are glimpses into her struggles in life, this book is a haven of tranquil thought, reflection and teaching. <br /><br />Lavendar has an almost childlike innocence that shines though this book. Her belief that grief can be our teacher and that we can learn important lessons through suffering is proudly displayed throughout. This book is a timely reminder that we can find positives despite and as a result of emotional pain, making us more empathic to others. Lavendar is a survivor of bereavement grief and with this book she uses that as a gift to uplift others in times of need. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="612877259523051581" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


